These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-1::.
4 different games are played: monopoly, whist, bridge, snooker
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: animation, documentary, family, mystery
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: february, april, may, december
There are 4 different favourite beverages: cola, lemonade, hot-chocolate, iced-tea
 1. the person who's birthday is in april is not to the right of the person who's birthday is in february##8
 2. the person drinking cola is not to the left of the person drinking cola##8
 3. the person drinking iced-tea is on the far left or far right##3
 4. the person who's birthday is in february is not to the left of the person who's birthday is in december##8
 5. the person drinking cola is not to the right of the person drinking cola##8
 6. the person watching family movies is on the right of the person who's birthday is in december##1
 7. the person playing whist is somewhere to the right of the person playing monopoly##5
 8. the person watching mystery movies is between the person drinking lemonade and the person who's birthday is in april##2
 9. the person drinking iced-tea is the person watching family movies##1
10. the person drinking iced-tea is on the right of the person playing snooker##1
11. the person playing bridge is on the left or right of the person watching animation movies##3
12. the person playing snooker is somewhere to the right of the person playing whist##5
13. the person watching family movies is not to the left of the person drinking iced-tea##8
14. the person playing whist is the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
15. the person playing whist is not the person who's birthday is in april##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |      3      |    4    |
| Game         | monopoly     | whist   | snooker | bridge |
| Movie-Genre   | documentary | mystery   | animation   | family  |
| Birthday         | april  | may  | december  | february |
| Beverage     | cola    | hot-chocolate | lemonade     | iced-tea    |

