.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: lemonade, milk, sprite, water
City: hannover, liverpool, berlin, san-francisco
The people have 4 different jobs:  fisherman, videographer, librarian, lawyer
There are 4 different nationalities: british, nigerian, chinese, turkish
 1. the librarian is between the british and the videographer##2
 2. the person drinking milk is not to the right of the nigerian##8
 3. the person drinking milk is on the left or right of the person traveling to hannover##3
 4. the person drinking lemonade is not to the right of the turkish##8
 5. the british is not to the left of the videographer##8
 6. the person traveling to san-francisco is not to the right of the person drinking water##8
 7. the chinese is somewhere to the left of the turkish##5
 8. the chinese is in an odd position##4
 9. the fisherman is the nigerian##1
10. the librarian is on the left or right of the british##3
11. the british is not to the left of the librarian##8
12. the person drinking water is on the left of the person drinking milk##1
13. the lawyer is somewhere to the right of the person traveling to liverpool##5
14. the videographer is on the left or right of the librarian##3
15. the person drinking lemonade is on the far left or far right##3
16. the person traveling to berlin is on the right of the person traveling to hannover##1
17. the person drinking lemonade is not to the right of the videographer##8
18. the person traveling to liverpool is not to the right of the nigerian##8
19. the person drinking water is on the right of the person traveling to liverpool##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2    |   3    |   4   |
| Beverage      | lemonade | sprite | water  | milk  |
| City          | san-francisco     | liverpool | hannover | berlin  |
| Job   | videographer    | librarian  | lawyer | fisherman |
| Nationality           | chinese | turkish | british    | nigerian  |

