.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-3::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: balloon-flower, dahlia, rose, lily
There 4 different types of food: peach, pear, papaya, artichoke
4 different games are played: monopoly, backgammon, snooker, go
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: climbing, cycling, sailing, surfing
 1. the person who's sport is climbing is on the right of the person who growsballoon-flower##1
 2. the person who growsdahlia is somewhere to the right of the person who growsrose##5
 3. the person who growslily is somewhere to the left of the person eating artichoke##5
 4. the person who growsrose is somewhere to the right of the person playing monopoly##5
 5. the person who's sport is sailing is not to the right of the person eating peach##8
 6. the person who growslily is not to the left of the person eating papaya##8
 7. the person playing snooker is in an odd position##4
 8. the person eating papaya is on the left of the person eating artichoke##1
 9. the person eating artichoke is on the left of the person eating pear##1
10. the person who's sport is cycling is on the far right##1
11. the person eating peach is not to the left of the person playing backgammon##8
12. the person eating artichoke is on the left or right of the person who's sport is cycling##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |     3     |     4      |
| Flower         | balloon-flower    | lily   | rose | dahlia |
| Food   | peach     | papaya  | artichoke   | pear      |
| Game   | backgammon | monopoly    | snooker      | go       |
| Sport         | sailing    | climbing | surfing   | cycling    |

