.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-4::.
There 4 different types of food: apple, banana, cucumber, plum
4 different games are played: mah-jongg, monopoly, go, bridge
City: edinburgh, prague, hannover, london
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: old-henry, fonseca, dannemann, havana
 1. the person playing go is not the person traveling to edinburgh##6
 2. the person traveling to london is on the left or right of the dannemann-smoker##3
 3. the person eating plum is the person traveling to hannover##1
 4. the person eating banana is between the person traveling to edinburgh and the person traveling to prague##2
 5. the person playing go is on the left or right of the old-henry-smoker##3
 6. the old-henry-smoker is not to the right of the person eating banana##8
 7. the person playing bridge is in an odd position##4
 8. the person playing go is somewhere to the right of the person playing mah-jongg##5
 9. the person playing bridge is on the right of the person traveling to london##1
10. the person traveling to prague is the old-henry-smoker##1
11. the fonseca-smoker is not to the right of the person eating apple##8
12. the person traveling to edinburgh is on the left or right of the fonseca-smoker##3
13. the person playing go is on the right of the person playing mah-jongg##1
14. the person traveling to prague is on the left or right of the fonseca-smoker##3
15. the person playing mah-jongg is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |         2          |    3    |    4     |
| Food    | cucumber    | banana             | apple   | plum     |
| Game   | mah-jongg | go            | bridge | monopoly    |
| City     | prague | london | edinburgh  | hannover |
| Cigar   | old-henry  | fonseca               | dannemann  | havana   |

