 2. the russian is the person playing billiard##1
 3. the photographer is not the person playing mah-jongg##6
 4. the writer is on the left of the person who growspoppy##1
 5. the person who growslily is not to the right of the polish##8
 6. the analyst is not to the right of the person who growslily##8
 7. the photographer is not to the left of the person playing billiard##8
 8. the malaysian is the person who growsrose##1
 9. the british is not to the left of the person playing bridge##8
10. the person who growspoppy is not to the left of the person who growslily##8
11. the security-guard is between the person playing bridge and the person who growsrose##2
12. the person playing mah-jongg is on the right of the analyst##1
13. the malaysian is not to the right of the person who growsrose##8
14. the photographer is on the left or right of the person who growsrose##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |     3     |    4     |
