 3. the person driving the bus is not to the left of the davidoff-smoker##8
 4. the chaman-smoker is somewhere to the right of the davidoff-smoker##5
 5. the person driving the scooter is the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
 6. the dannemann-smoker is not to the right of the person who's hobby is traveling##8
 7. the bongani-smoker is not the person who's hobby is woodworking##6
 8. the fan of ambient is somewhere between the person driving the scooter and the bongani-smoker##7
 9. the person driving the scooter is somewhere to the right of the fan of ambient##5
10. the person driving the van is on the left or right of the fan of ambient##3
11. the fan of reggae is on the right of the fan of indie##1
12. the fan of ambient is not the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##6
13. the person who's hobby is traveling is somewhere to the right of the bongani-smoker##5
14. the chaman-smoker is on the left of the dannemann-smoker##1
15. the person driving the bus is not to the right of the fan of ambient##8

.:: Answer ::.
