The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: comedy, drama, scientific, fantasy
The people have 4 different jobs:  electrician, librarian, social-worker, videographer
4 different games are played: scrabble, bridge, whist, go
 1. the librarian is on the left or right of the videographer##3
 2. the person playing scrabble is not the person watching comedy movies##6
 3. the person playing go is somewhere to the left of the person watching comedy movies##5
 4. the social-worker is the person who's birthday is in july##1
 5. the person who's birthday is in april is in an even position##4
 6. the person playing go is somewhere between the person who's birthday is in august and the person who's birthday is in february##7
 7. the person playing go is not to the left of the person playing whist##8
 8. the person playing bridge is somewhere between the person watching scientific movies and the person watching drama movies##7
 9. the electrician is on the far left or far right##3
10. the librarian is not to the left of the librarian##8
11. the electrician is on the far left##1
12. the videographer is on the far right##1
13. the person playing go is the person watching scientific movies##1
14. the person watching scientific movies is not to the left of the person who's birthday is in february##8
15. the person playing bridge is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in july##5
16. the librarian is not to the left of the person watching fantasy movies##8

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1      |       2       |     3      |      4       |
