 3. the person who likes lavender is not the person who's birthday is in august##6
 4. the victorian house is not to the left of the person who likes white##8
 5. the person who likes mauve is not to the right of the person watching musical movies##8
 6. the person who's birthday is in june is on the left of the person who's birthday is in march##1
