 3. the person watching musical movies is the person who's sport is badminton##1
 4. the person watching thriller movies is not to the right of the person watching musical movies##8
 5. the person driving the bike is between the person driving the train and the person who's sport is volleyball##2
 6. the person who's hobby is skydiving is not to the left of the person who's hobby is camping##8
 7. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the left of the person who's sport is badminton##1
 8. the person watching spy movies is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is skydiving##5
 9. the person driving the taxi is not the person who's hobby is chess##6
10. the person who's hobby is skydiving is in an even position##4
11. the person watching thriller movies is not to the left of the person driving the bike##8
12. the person who's hobby is chess is on the left of the person watching satire movies##1
13. the person driving the bike is on the left or right of the person watching musical movies##3
