 4. the person traveling to hannover is somewhere to the right of the person traveling to paris##5
 5. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left or right of the person who growsballoon-flower##3
 6. the person drinking lemonade is on the right of the person traveling to hannover##1
 7. the person traveling to san-francisco is between the person traveling to hannover and the person drinking juice##2
 8. the person drinking mirinda is in an odd position##4
 9. the owner of the horse is not to the right of the person traveling to hannover##8
10. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left or right of the owner of the horse##3
11. the person who growsdaffodil is not to the left of the owner of the goldfish##8
12. the person traveling to venice is on the right of the person who growsazalea##1
13. the owner of the horse is not to the left of the person drinking juice##8
14. the owner of the goldfish is on the right of the person who growsazalea##1
